translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_93307587:
    # mc "Dude, I've a problem..."
    mc "Bro, gue ada masalah..."

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_13b792d8:
    # "Игорь" "And you've come here to have me solve it for you?"
    "Игорь" "Dan lo datang ke sini biar gue yang nyelesain buat lo?"

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_ae5de6aa:
    # mc "No, but I expected you to help me."
    mc "Nggak, tapi gue berharap lo bantu gue."

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_beff22cd:
    # mc "Two morons have occupied my place by the shop. Let's go fuck them."
    mc "Dua orang tolol ngerebut tempat gue di dekat toko. Ayo kita hajar mereka."

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_abbe9c4f:
    # "Игорь" "Sorry, man, but I'm already doing your job."
    "Игорь" "Maaf, men, tapi gue sudah ngerjain kerjaan lo."

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_b668d8dd:
    # mc "Alright. Maybe you could give me some advice at least?"
    mc "Oke. Setidaknya lo bisa kasih gue saran?"

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_2ecb11e4:
    # "Игорь" "Use something heavy you could bash their heads with."
    "Игорь" "Pakai benda berat buat ngehantam kepala mereka."

translate indonesian ep2_4_5_igor_82cb25ac:
    # mc "Just as I thought."
    mc "Persis seperti dugaan gue."
